Nutrient data for: MILKA CHOCOLATE OREO COOKIES AND CREME 100 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622300631574
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, vegetable fats (palm, palm kernel), cocoa butter, skimmed MILK powder, whey powder (from MILK), WHEAT flour, cocoa mass, MILK fat, fat-reduced cocoa powder (0.7%), emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), WHEAT starch, HAZELNUT paste, raising agents (potassium hydrogen carbonate, ammonium hydrogen carbonate, sodium hydrogen carbonate), salt, flavourings, contains glucose syrup and/or glucose-fructose syrup. Milk solids: 18% minimum in the Alpine milk chocolate. MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS. Date available: 05/18/2018 Date last updated by company: 05/18/2018
